0%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB316-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%9D/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Nov 2020 22:02:37 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-11-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB316-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%B9%9D/</guid><description>驱散想像,克制欲望,消除嗜好,把支配能力保持在它自己的力量范围之内。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻315-沉思录八</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-10-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB315-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E5%85%AB/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Nov 2020 22:23:33 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-10-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB315-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E5%85%AB/</guid><description>一个人做适合于一个人做的工作对他就是满足。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻314-沉思录七</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-09-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB314-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%83/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Nov 2020 23:00:55 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-09-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB314-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%83/</guid><description>不要让将来的事困扰你,因为如果那是必然要发生的话,你将带着你现在对待当前事物的同样理性走向它们。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻313-沉思录六</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-08-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB313-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E5%85%AD/</link><pubDate>Sun, 08 Nov 2020 10:57:12 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-08-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB313-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E5%85%AD/</guid><description>宇宙的实体是忠顺和服从的,那支配着它的理性自身没有任何原因行恶,因为它毫无恶意, 它也不对任何事物行恶, 不损害任何事物。 而所有的事物都是根据这一理性而创造而完善的。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻312-沉思录五</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-07-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB312-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%BA%94/</link><pubDate>Sat, 07 Nov 2020 12:12:56 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-07-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB312-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%BA%94/</guid><description>想想普遍的实体,你只占有它很少的一部分;想想普遍的时间,你只分到它一个短暂和不可分的间隔;想想那被命运所确定的东西,你是它多么小的一部分。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻311-沉思录四</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-06-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB311-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E5%9B%9B/</link><pubDate>Fri, 06 Nov 2020 23:21:15 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-06-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB311-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E5%9B%9B/</guid><description>不要思绪纷乱, 而是在每个行动中都尊重正义, 对每一印象都坚持运用领悟或理解的能力。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻310-沉思录三</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-05-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB310-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%89/</link><pubDate>Thu, 05 Nov 2020 23:00:07 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-05-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB310-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%89/</guid><description>当你不把你的思想指向公共福利的某个目标时, 不要把你剩下的生命浪费在思考别人上。因为,当你有这思想时,你就丧失了做别的事情的机会。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻309-沉思录二</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-04-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB309-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%BA%8C/</link><pubDate>Wed, 04 Nov 2020 23:29:17 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-04-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB309-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%BA%8C/</guid><description>不要去注意别人心里在想什么,一个人就很少会被看成是不幸福的,而那些不注意他们自己内心的活动的人却必然是不幸的。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻308-沉思录一</title><link>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-03-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB308-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%80/</link><pubDate>Tue, 03 Nov 2020 23:09:39 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://book.asxing.com/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95/2020-11-03-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB308-%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%80/</guid><description>自己与自己的对话, 自己说服自己, 自然也就不需要过分讲究词藻、 注意交代和安排结构,而集中注意于一种思想的深入和行进。</description></item></channel></rss>